   4:../bootloader/src/main.c ****   * @brief   Bootloader main program for STM32F401
   5:../bootloader/src/main.c ****   * @details This bootloader initializes the system and jumps to the application
   6:../bootloader/src/main.c ****   *          located at 0x08010000 if valid. Otherwise, it stays in bootloader mode.
